          viewlet for Plone 5 (rather than a template slot). [djowett-ftw]
        
        - Work around duplication of the `plone.globalstatusmessage` viewlet.
          (See https://github.com/plone/Products.CMFPlone/issues/2947)
          [djowett-ftw]
        
        
        1.6.2 (2017-08-22)
